    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/04cd325f19451b99f169205638268672.avif?t=1711373613\" width=600 height=426 /></span><br><br>A childhood dream comes true. Play with your remote controlled tank, dash in the arena and eliminate others to become that last tank standing! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/e810d5eb387b4ac69a02aeeefee40780.avif?t=1711373613\" width=600 height=236 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DODGE. JUMP, SHOOT &amp; DESTROY!</h2><br>BUMPER TANKS is a 4-player local &amp; online party game inspired by the classic couch multiplayer genre. It's all about intense versus matches that are easy to jump into, but difficult to truly master. You'll need serious skills to emerge victorious from the fierce tank battles that ensue. So gather your friends, grab some snacks, and get ready for some seriously blasting gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/10e564930e6bf4814fd5ae77b52e18b2.poster.avif?t=1711373613\" width=616 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/10e564930e6bf4814fd5ae77b52e18b2.webm?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/10e564930e6bf4814fd5ae77b52e18b2.mp4?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/17cfd2ec4300181534a946cc1e1216ad.poster.avif?t=1711373613\" width=616 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/17cfd2ec4300181534a946cc1e1216ad.webm?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/17cfd2ec4300181534a946cc1e1216ad.mp4?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/c83b2c58e0cfed2f37490234fd3a1909.poster.avif?t=1711373613\" width=616 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/c83b2c58e0cfed2f37490234fd3a1909.webm?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/c83b2c58e0cfed2f37490234fd3a1909.mp4?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/7e8cb3f707d68b830687c5df40f24b21.poster.avif?t=1711373613\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/7e8cb3f707d68b830687c5df40f24b21.webm?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/7e8cb3f707d68b830687c5df40f24b21.mp4?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/2a91ebac93f728978db8c60871cdbb6c.poster.avif?t=1711373613\" width=616 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366050/extras/2a91ebac93f728978db8c60871cdbb6c.webm?t=1711373613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=v